=== Analysis Plan

    - Primary analysis: ANCOVA comparing 6-month DSQ-PEM change across arms, adjusted for baseline severity and sex
    - Post-hoc pairwise comparisons with Bonferroni correction (Brain First vs.\ Mast Cell First; Brain First vs.\ Metabolic First)
    - Secondary analyses: Per-protocol analysis for patients with $gt.eq$80% medication adherence
    - Trajectory analysis: Quadratic mixed-effects models for symptom change over 6 months


